input tree and provenance structure
===================================

Overview
--------

The upstream production code writes two persistent trees that are relevant to
this repository:

  EventSelectionFilter
  SubRun

The EventSelectionFilter tree is the event-level analysis ntuple.

The SubRun tree is the subrun-level normalization and exposure tree.

The production code can also write event-weight information either as branches
on EventSelectionFilter or, if configured, in a separate EventWeights tree.

