Notes on EventWeightAnalysis:

  The exact set of weight branches depends on configuration flags such as
  createMapBranch, createFluxBranch, createGenieBranch, createReintBranch,
  createSplineBranch, createTuneBranch, createSplineTimesTuneBranch,
  createPPFXBranch, and createGenieUpDnVecs.

  The weights map can include combined products like:

    All_UBGenie
    reint_all
    ppfx_all
    flux_all

  as well as individual named weight vectors copied from the art
  MCEventWeight products.

EventWeights
------------

If EventWeightAnalysis is configured with createDedicatedTree=true, it also
writes a separate EventWeights tree containing:

  run                int
  subRun             int
  evt                int
